name: ut-registration-api
description: - Uses get and post requests with query params, works using forms basically no scripts   - `searchCheck()` runs on main form submit, changes endpoint depending on command   - `validateForm()` only on acknowledgement page, checks to see if box checked -

scripts.docs: npx typedoc --excludeInternal --excludePrivate --plugin typedoc-plugin-markdown --out docs src/api.ts && cat docs/classes/RegistrationSession.md | sed 's/RegistrationSession.md/README.md/g' > docs/.README.docs.md && cat .README.header.md > README.md && tail -n +2 docs/.README.docs.md >> README.md && rm -rf docs
